channel.title: Essential Aura - A New PI Soon to be Worked on! - New Banner
channel.description:
[center][URL=http://img252.imageshack.us/i/23118805.png/][IMG]http://img252.imageshack.us/img252/158/23118805.png[/img][/URL] I really was dieing to try these new servers that are being released. I am kind of tired of using old servers nobody uses (such as Realm Onwards with its Runelive). This time I am deciding to use a more popular source, InsidiaX v2. this way, I can use more modern code. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Minigames[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has newly improved minigames such as Pest Control, Fight Pits, Fight Caves, and the Dual Arena. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]All Combat Skills Working[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has 100% Melee, Range, Magic, and Summoning. Also, Essential Aura has a better combat system than usual servers. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]High Stability[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura is very stable, with all these features, its still one of the most stable servers. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Skilling System[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has the best Skilling System in town. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Player Titles[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has Player Tiles which you will grasp your hands for. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Dungeoneering[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has the most state of the art Dungeoneering. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Curses[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has 100% Working Curses. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]New Hitmarks[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has the new hitmarks - fading, floating, critical, and fonts! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Wilderness Revernants[/b][/li][/ul] Get your Revenaunt gear on as Revenaunts are back in town! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]A Nice Money Making Way - Red Dragons[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has a money making way called PKing Dragons. This area is in lvl 47 wilderness and also has Red Dragons that drop rares. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]A Custom Skill For You PKing Fans[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has a custom skill called the PKing skill. The skill raises each time you kill a player. Work your way up to be the best PKer ever! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Elite Slayer Tasks[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has Elite Slayer Tasks for those Slayer lovers! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]A New Person Awaits Every Corner[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has NPC's all around the world! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Overloads[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has 100% Overloads. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Charging[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has Dragon Fire Shields charging perfectly! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Working PVP Armours[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura honors our PKers, so we give them PVP Armours! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]90% Correct Item Stats[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has almost all our armours up-to-date through Item Stats. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Get Your Own Shop[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura gives you the power to be like an NPC and have your own shop! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Ring of Life & Slayer Helmet Effects[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura had all Ring of Life & Slayer Helmet Effects! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Autocast[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has a New RS Autocast Feature! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]All Effects[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has Torva, Korasi, Primal, Spirit Shields, Hand Cannon, Arcane Stream, Ring of Vigour, and Chaotic Weapons effects! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Dungeoneering Emote[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has perfect emotes for the Dungeoneering Cape! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]GFX Rendering[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has GFX Rendering so that it looks smoother! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Accurate Special Calculators[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has very, yes, near perfect Special Calculators. [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]New RS Money Bag[/b][/li][/ul] Essential Aura has the new RS Money Bag, store your money, be happy! [ul][li][color=goldenrod][b]Gameframe Changer![/b][/li][/ul] Theres a gameframe for old-school, middle-school, and new-school!
